### 4. Get Dashboard Stats
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. List Students (Paginated)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/students?skip=0&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}